^ResearchScout|description:Autonomous research scout with deterministic trace _|

#query|safety constraints for open world agents _|
#sources|arxiv,docs,benchmarks _|
#status|running _|

!|log:Scout query:#query _|
!|#sources
    #source|#stream _|
    !|trace:probe @loop.count #source _|
    !|log:Collected note from #source _|
_|

#status|complete _|
!?|#status:complete
    !|log:Scout finished with traceable steps _|
_|
?!|
    !|warn:Scout incomplete _|
_|
